  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK542">
<l>vāṉōkki vāḻu mulakellā maṉṉavaṉ </l>
<l>kōṉōkki vāḻuṅ kuṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When there is rain, the living creation thrives; and so when the king rules justly, his subjects thrive.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
